{"tid":251388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（無間道）美CIA有內鬼，12名埋係中國間諜被殺","createTime":"2017-05-21T00:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T09:22:30.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e444813d8a5708ae7b206284d26e8bab2ad75f","tid":251388,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T00:01:33.000Z","msg":"《紐約時報》引述美國官員報導，中國在兩年內殺害或囚禁18至20個美國中央情報局（CIA）的線民，有系統地瓦解中情局在中國的間諜網。<br />\n報導指，自2010至2012年，至少12名向CIA提供情報的消息人士，在中國遇害，令CIA在中國境內多年的情報網被摧毀。美國官員透露，一名線民在一座政府建築物外被槍殺，是中國當局刻意安排，以警告其他為美國提供情報的人。<br />\n《紐時》稱，2010年之前，CIA在中國的間諜工作，曾取得大量有價值的情報，但2010年底起情報數量大減，先是有線民失蹤，隨著有更多線民被殺。線民的損失規模之大，是數十年來少有的。聯邦調查局（FBI）已和CIA展開聯手調查，目前無法確定是不是CIA有內奸出賣線民，或是中國當局中國破解了CIA與線民秘密聯絡的方法或暗號。<br />\n在調查美國駐北京大使館所有僱員後，當局懷疑一名前CIA特工最可疑，他曾負責管理監視中國的部門，離開CIA後，決定與家人留在亞洲，並且轉行經商。調查人員推測，這是中國情報人員為他鋪定後路，只是目前還沒有足夠證據。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170521/1122926/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170521%2F1122926%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=a388e225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170521/1122926/</a><br />\n美國埋左咁多間諜係中國，中國又埋返一個卧底係CIA,好有戲味"},{"pid":"fd5d5d3f46aee81b38ee644c0f906a1ee9873137","tid":251388,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T00:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/080457_e4d5b17ec956ba730d696fa98e0fa495.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F080457_e4d5b17ec956ba730d696fa98e0fa495.jpg&h=30519274&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51a16cab9cd3c2b8d71efb5dc02c70efb1ad236e","tid":251388,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T00:27:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaadacd7a57b6e93d64cddd45eb92e0c1a2f360","tid":251388,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:07:21.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】北京一直強烈不滿美國駐港總領事館在港收集政治材料，但本報從維基解密公開的美國機密外交電文發現，特首梁振英「心腹」、中央政策組首席顧問邵善波原來與美領館過從甚密，於2009年向美方「爆料」，披露北京對香港政改底線、曾蔭權承諾任內解決雙普選未獲中央授意，以及在十二五規劃中，港府與港澳辦、法改委閉門會議情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121206/18092377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20121206%2F18092377&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0aede407\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20121206%2F18092377&h=062795a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121206/18092377</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時捉佢犬決<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2ee258f1f38487ae6357746fec137dc7690499","tid":251388,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"係香港整個CIA 悼念會先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6e912f46fd50cf2d98f83c08bda69521f57ec8","tid":251388,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b83cbee21d716be9e6d3099e27675a7b8080bc","tid":251388,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:27:55.000Z","msg":"離開CIA <br />\n<br />\n仲同家人係亞洲經商<br />\n<br />\n根本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318d6952cdd2f407654fd45cd4181eeaff868779","tid":251388,"uid":73111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"死亡筆記"},{"pid":"9774769d6d3e2f58f8b73fcfe5defa9df538919e","tid":251388,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>離開CIA <br />\n<br />\n仲同家人係亞洲經商<br />\n<br />\n根本<img src